Package: mdthemes
Title: Markdown Themes for 'ggplot2'
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Thomas", "Neitmann", , "r-pkgs@thomasadventure.blog", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: A collection of 'ggplot2' themes that render text as
    markdown/HTML. This enables the creation of complex formatted plot
    labels, e.g. titles with individual words highlighted in different
    colors.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/thomas-neitmann/mdthemes,
    https://thomas-neitmann.github.io/mdthemes/
BugReports: https://github.com/thomas-neitmann/mdthemes/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    cowplot,
    ggplot2 (>= 3.3.0),
    ggtext,
    ggthemes,
    hrbrthemes,
    tvthemes
Suggests:
    glue,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Config/testthat/edition: 3
